    <p>Hy-phen-ation made easy</p>

    <section>
      <h3>Presentation</h3>
      <p>
        Pyphen is a pure Python module to hyphenate words using included or
        external Hunspell hyphenation dictionaries. It includes by default the
        dictionaries distributed by LibreOffice.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>100% pure Python with no dependencies</li>
        <li>caches dict files and hyphenated words</li>
        <li>supports nonstandard hyphenation patterns</li>
        <li>a lot of included dictionaries:
          <ul>
            <li>Afrikaans</li>
            <li>Bulgarian</li>
            <li>Catalan</li>
            <li>Croatian</li>
            <li>Czech</li>
            <li>Danish</li>
